蹴鞠是現代足球最早的形式，但現代足球並不是由蹴鞠所演化而來，<span style=\"color: red;\">國際足球協會在2004年確認足球起源於中國山東</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"所謂發源地，係咪要有比賽或者規則先叫發源地？如果阿豬阿狗踢兩腳波都叫發源地，咁人類由識行開始已經周圍踢野，全世界都有好多發源地，點解一定係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:17:19.000Z","msg":"因為FIFA收咗支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebae4a0996a3d9d6ba23da84463c595cfa47c5f","tid":764190,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"唔好開心住，英國咁奶共，如果同支共入咗頭一二位競爭時，隨時棄權讓比支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54add56b2fbcb7616f31533993eb25c8e67c3e47","tid":764190,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebae4a0996a3d9d6ba23da84463c595cfa47c5f","tid":764190,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"唔好開心住，英國咁奶共，如果同支共入咗頭一二位競爭時，隨時棄權讓比支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲要脫埋歐<br />\n嗰啲票數mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cb811aa4e854c258b3a6d20ddd5dc96e6f65b2","tid":764190,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"比支那好，我想睇國際大笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af031fb0c6e9938afb5eddc97231f8be40ab9b93","tid":764190,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7cb811aa4e854c258b3a6d20ddd5dc96e6f65b2","tid":764190,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite